  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced shallots and cook until they are lightly browned.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the dashi extract and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add the jasmine rice and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cover the saucepan.",
    "Cook for 18 minutes or until the rice is tender.",
    "Fluff the rice with a fork and stir in the cooked tofu.",
    "Transfer the rice to a serving platter and garnish with chopped scallions."
